    "causal_summary": "No skill exists for AI assistants to delegate tasks to GitHub's Copilot CLI (`copilot`). The project has 3 CLI orchestration skills (cli-gemini, cli-codex, cli-claude-code) but no equivalent for Copilot CLI. This leaves Copilot's unique capabilities — multi-provider model selection (7+ models from Anthropic, OpenAI, Google), cloud delegation (`/delegate`), collaborative plan mode, autopilot execution, and repository memory — inaccessible to external orchestrators.",
